# --- Secrets & credentials: NEVER commit (belt-and-suspenders) -----------------
# Real secrets live in Cloudflare Worker secrets / KV, the VPS's EnvironmentFile,
# ~/.appstoreconnect + the keychain, GitHub Actions secrets, and macapp/.release.env
# — NOT in the repo. See SECURITY.md for the full inventory + rotation steps.
# NB: .gitignore has NO inline comments — each pattern MUST be alone on its line.
macapp/.release.env
# wrangler's local secret file (any worker dir)
.dev.vars
# local env files (a stray .release.env / .env), but keep templates + RN's base
*.env
!*.env.example
!.xcode.env
# private keys & signing material
*.p8
*.p12
*.pem
*.key
# App Store Connect API keys (default name) + SSH private keys
AuthKey_*
id_rsa*
